{"tid":2221009,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安無阻止 校方拒報警  港大縱容藍絲拆牆 學生會強烈譴責","createTime":"2020-09-28T05:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T06:42:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"084e76ced717b990e7f23edbe6c03ea2e1835954","tid":2221009,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/T2MG2FD2MJFBHMXPDWRKEJKAZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FT2MG2FD2MJFBHMXPDWRKEJKAZ4%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIXPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=2046f72c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FT2MG2FD2MJFBHMXPDWRKEJKAZ4%2F&h=f09dd3d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/T2MG2FD2MJFBHMXPDWRKEJKAZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保安無阻止 校方拒報警 <br />\n港大縱容藍絲拆牆 學生會強烈譴責<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一批鄉音大媽大叔前晚浩浩蕩蕩闖進香港大學校園，撕毀四幅連儂牆，又推倒學生會旗幟，高呼：「唔希望自己嘅仔女喺咁唔乾淨嘅大學入面讀書」，更拍下「偉大戰績」放上網，多名在場港大保安未有制止。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：紅衞兵fb圍爐晒戰績<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QTgJgJ1HCQO5dE6VPEDSrGCD0Kc=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VOG4V65ODFBYVFFNZMEYQGJGSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQTgJgJ1HCQO5dE6VPEDSrGCD0Kc%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVOG4V65ODFBYVFFNZMEYQGJGSM.jpg&h=45dee712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大學生會長葉芷琳斥涉事藍絲撕毀校園財產，又指保安未有盡責阻止。<br />\n<br />\n前晚事發後，有港大學生趕赴現場，惟破壞者已揚長而去，遂留低清理垃圾，該學生表明喜愛港大，哽咽斥責：「佢哋（藍絲）成日話『唔好攪亂人地生活，唔好周圍破壞』，但點解佢哋又做緊呢啲咁可惡既事情呢？殺人放火金腰帶！」另有同學修復部份連儂牆，坦言對保安的不作為感憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨本報記者再到場了解，至少兩名非裔保安在港鐵香港大學站出口位置站崗，他們大聲喝止記者採訪，更拍打記者手部，態度惡劣。記者要求與其上司理論，但等了約20分鐘仍未見人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/atwY5Ui57_gQqcV-9I9hPjIEmgU=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RQ2676547NEPHHS53A5BDSNMZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FatwY5Ui57_gQqcV-9I9hPjIEmgU%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRQ2676547NEPHHS53A5BDSNMZA.jpg&h=4ad35699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨晨本報記者到場採訪，被港大兩名非裔保安大聲喝止，更遭拍打手部。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明午重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n據悉，港大去年就抗爭運動加強保安，有傳聘請外籍保安花費逾百萬元。港大學生會會長葉芷琳直言：「完全唔理解校方點解要用咁大筆錢去請啲做唔到嘢嘅保安」，又透露兩個多月前也有人撕毀連儂牆，事後她與保安部面談，對方指「會盡力改善」，惟前晚又發生同類事件。葉又斥該批藍絲對學生惡言相向，撕毀校園財產，更將破壞片段放上網，對此感極度憤怒，予以強烈譴責。學生會成員昨已重新掛回學生會旗幟，明午會重建連儂牆，呼籲同學參與。<br />\n<br />\n市民陳先生居於港大附近，亦曾在港大就讀課程，前晚從網上新聞獲知事件。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，港大昨未有報警求助。但警方指留意到網上流傳在薄扶林道一大學校園內發生的片段，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示對同類破壞行徑屢次在校園發生深感遺憾，強調任何組織或人士都不。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9e203fcbf26bf06cdf196d5983e6166567758bdc","tid":2221009,"uid":194005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，除非你係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4166e9db58723b266b13e43e8e0ae8c04f2bffb6","tid":2221009,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4bfce8ac668e9c25006457ade47d3225899c56","tid":2221009,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b24ed94562f6a5fa0883a10689d99d4488c94b","tid":2221009,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e203fcbf26bf06cdf196d5983e6166567758bdc","tid":2221009,"uid":194005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1